mod SPEC2MAUDE-GENERATED is
  protecting BOOL .
  protecting NAT .
  protecting INT .
  protecting RAT .
  protecting FLOAT .
  protecting STRING .
  protecting QID .

  --- origin: <Spec2Maude minimal runtime prelude> / prelude / Prelude
