  --- origin: <Spec2Maude minimal runtime prelude> / prelude / Prelude
  sort RecordItem .

  --- origin: <Spec2Maude minimal runtime prelude> / prelude / Prelude
  sort RecordItems .

  --- origin: <Spec2Maude minimal runtime prelude> / prelude / Prelude
  subsort RecordItem < RecordItems .

  --- origin: <Spec2Maude minimal runtime prelude> / prelude / Prelude
  op EMPTY : -> RecordItem .

  --- origin: <Spec2Maude minimal runtime prelude> / prelude / Prelude
  op _;_ : RecordItems RecordItems -> RecordItems [ctor assoc id: EMPTY] .

